<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/248903-is-this-appropriate-for-a-girl-who-loves">Is this appropriate for a girl who loves dogs and is interested in the Holocaust?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_248903'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13593012-trusting-calvin">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/248903-is-this-appropriate-for-a-girl-who-loves">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/248903-is-this-appropriate-for-a-girl-who-loves">See all 2 answers</a>
