<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think a little bit older would be better, but it depends on the girl. She would definitely like the part about Calvin and the other dogs. The part a<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think a little bit older would be better, but it depends on the girl. She would definitely like the part about Calvin and the other dogs. The part about the holocaust might be hard, but is necessary to really understand the later part with the dogs.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
